## ğŸ¯ Final Thoughts

> ğŸ§  **If the client is a browser**, you can choose SSR or CSR based on your needs.  
> ğŸ¤– **If the client is not a browser**, always use APIs and return raw data (JSON).  
> ğŸ’¡ Use consistent endpoints, proper status codes, and separation of concerns between UI and data layers.

